casebody.data:
Schuyler Hanson, Respondent, v. Queensboro Farm Products, Inc., Appellant.

Reported below, 265 App. Div. 819.

Submitted November 23, 1942; decided December 10, 1942. Nathan A. Goldenthal for motion. Charles K. Finch opposed.

Motion dismissed, with ten dollars costs and necessary printing disbursements on the ground that the orders do not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
